{"tid":1229083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實617三罷係最好手段","createTime":"2019-06-15T20:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T14:08:32.000Z","uid":88813,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c5cd6cf63f8ef3d513693214d6382d8d130dbe35","tid":1229083,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T20:56:00.000Z","msg":"睇返我哋訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1/ 撤回修例<br />\n2/ 為612事件正名<br />\n3/ 追究警隊濫暴<br />\n<br />\n其實2 同3 都唔適合用衝擊做手段<br />\n一衝，警察實要暴力清場<br />\n<br />\n用暴力逼佢唔定性612係暴動？<br />\n用暴力逼佢克制自己唔亂打人唔亂開槍？<br />\n諗落就覺得唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n617三罷係用和平手段施壓<br />\n而且我諗好多人依家真係冇心機車返工返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民陣唔搞，自己可以繼續呼籲<br />\n<br />\n咁三罷當日做乜好？<br />\n或者可以約埋默站為犧牲者默哀<br />\n反送中工作要繼續做，解釋暫緩不等於撤回<br />\n同時打悲情牌繼續文宣戰<br />\n話畀全香港人知警隊如何失控<br />\n話畀全香港人知犧牲者竟要以死相諫<br />\n希望有傳媒報導加大宣傳效果<br />\n<br />\n只係少少提議，大家幫手諗<br />\n林鄭想拖，我哋就必須繼續進攻<br />\n但依家戰場唔係街頭，係民心所向<br />\n加油，今次場仗許勝不許敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653b4c9ef5c41bac3cf284ffa62e996ed3e9e7c8","tid":1229083,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T20:58:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a07bdaaa7a09bf2bd0fbfdb7cda229bd16461dc2","tid":1229083,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T21:03:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe993afb50f2c1c2a48222b8ae5db2125469cd1a","tid":1229083,"uid":65912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T21:03:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e32eda08fdb0419d7702db6e028db79568b45296","tid":1229083,"uid":255272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T21:10:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d7993937d87259d69bc57f05e67bff4a8b03a1f","tid":1229083,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T21:12:54.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n不合作運動一定要同時進行"},{"pid":"8ce5d9c09e7c455246c7bfa9e4f71ec71fc5a495","tid":1229083,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af541e1719157c457f352e2668b730e1d6e73a8e","tid":1229083,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>(突發）民陣成員再次發起617 三罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1229081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1229081</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7bed14765f53fb44c2224afc508f6ca784e50be2","tid":1229083,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"a2c7d9f0ef856b9cccc7025b8657a524770a485a","tid":1229083,"uid":88813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:08:32.000Z","msg":"特別係政府已進一步跪低，雖然我都唔收貨，但再衝民意隨時逆轉，想救義士要用其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}